BAFANA Bafana coach Shakes Mashaba called in Mamelodi Sundowns midfielder Tiyani Mabunda to replace injured Dean Furman.Bafana are in preparations in Limpopo for their must-win match against Senegal &nbsp;in the 2018 Russia Fifa World Cup qualifier on Saturday at Peter Mokaba Stadium (3pm). Furman was released from camp after sustaining a ribcage injury.Mashaba&rsquo;s charges suffered another blow when their left back Tebogo Langerman pulled a hamstring in a friendly and his replacement is yet to be announced.ALSO READ: BAFANA READY FOR WAR!